# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# QuickFile MCP — Environment Variables Reference
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# THIS FILE IS SAFE TO COMMIT — it contains no real values.
# It documents exactly which secrets you need to add.
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WHERE TO PUT YOUR REAL SECRETS:
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. GITHUB ACTIONS (CI + Auto-deploy)
#    Go to: https://github.com/Time-Plixer-Production/quickfile-mcp
#           → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions
#           → "New repository secret"
#
#    Add ALL of these:
#    ┌─────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
#    │ Secret Name             │ Where to find the value                      │
#    ├─────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────┤
#    │ QF_ACCOUNT_NUMBER       │ QuickFile dashboard → top right corner       │
#    │ QF_API_KEY              │ QuickFile → Account Settings → API Access    │
#    │ QF_APP_ID               │ QuickFile → Account Settings →               │
#    │                         │   Third Party Integrations → your app        │
#    │ CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN    │ dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens       │
#    │                         │   Use "Edit Cloudflare Workers" template     │
#    │ CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID   │ Cloudflare dashboard → sidebar Account ID    │
#    └─────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
#
#    Once added, every push to main will:
#      a) Run typecheck + tests (ci.yml)
#      b) Push QF secrets into the Worker encrypted vault
#      c) Deploy the Worker to Cloudflare (deploy.yml)
#
# 2. LOCAL DEVELOPMENT
#    Copy this file to .env (already in .gitignore) and fill in real values:
#      cp .env.example .env
#    Then edit .env with your actual credentials.
#
# 3. CLOUDFLARE WORKER (manual one-time setup if needed)
#    npx wrangler secret put QF_ACCOUNT_NUMBER
#    npx wrangler secret put QF_API_KEY
#    npx wrangler secret put QF_APP_ID
#    (The deploy workflow does this automatically — only needed for manual deploy)
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── QuickFile API credentials ─────────────────────────────────
QF_ACCOUNT_NUMBER=
QF_API_KEY=
QF_APP_ID=

# ── Cloudflare deployment ─────────────────────────────────────
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=

# ── Optional tuning (safe defaults shown) ────────────────────
LOG_LEVEL=info
RATE_LIMIT_OVERRIDE=
